headline: Buy These 5 3D Printing Stocks to Strengthen Your Portfolio for 2025
summary: Five 3D printing stocks have strong revenues and earnings growth potential for 2025 and solid short-term upside. These are: ADSK, NVDA, GE, LHX, CSR.

headline: RTX Signs $38M Deal to Support Navy's AN/SPY-6(V) Family of Radars
summary: RTX gets a contract from the Naval Sea Systems Command, WA, D.C., to aid the AN/SPY-6(V) Family of Radars.
